dad41","tid":2024543,"uid":193788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T16:23:00.000Z","msg":"目前黎睇就係24號既遊行<br />\n冇不反<br />\n<br />\n其實做終極和理非當去老銅行下街，有事就閃去食飯冇事就行<br />\n有冇人會出？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不了又送頭"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T19:52:14.000Z","msg":"老閪都出"},{"pid":"327360f6ae51fa317b18a0e38c5c9782b964751f","tid":2024543,"uid":235316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2e60a201a0eba1a1caeafaa6162829a4919dad41","tid":2024543,"uid":193788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T16:23:00.000Z","msg":"目前黎睇就係24號既遊行<br />\n冇不反<br />\n<br />\n其實做終極和理非當去老銅行下街，有事就閃去食飯冇事就行<br />\n有冇人會出？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不了又送頭"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T19:52:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ueOCFTV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FueOCFTV.png&h=773dc210&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n524 反惡歌法大遊行攻略<br />\n<br />\n為降低活動難度及風險，將會改為流水式遊行，沿軒尼詩道往來銅鑼灣東角道及灣仔修頓球場。<br />\n<br />\n集合時間: 5月24日 13:00pm<br />\n集合地點A: 銅鑼灣東角道Sogo外<br />\n集合地點B: 灣仔修頓球場<br />\n<br />\n預計黑警部署:<br />\n1) 在集合地點AB不停進行搜身防止人群聚集<br />\n2) 在上圖路線以及內街每個十字路口部署2隊防暴狗<br />\n3) 三部水炮車會分別部署在: 政總，狗總及北角狗屋<br />\n4) 有機會在AB兩點中間切開遊行路線<br />\n<br />\n解決方案:<br />\n1) 全民和理非，不帶任何危險物品<br />\n2) Be Water; 離離合合，合合離離; 聚有時，散有時。<br />\n3) 人數壓勝，人多就安全<br />\n4) 唔好羊群心態見到狗就跑，跟大隊唔好落單。<br />\n<br />\n香城Online<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/HKOnline2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FHKOnline2&d=Vmg9VhgMmKCDk1oLDtgP7rQTYXQauqfU4Ix09hrgZFI%3D&h=04372a7b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/HKOnline2</a>"},{"pid":"5e09fe3a74ecd18fe2740a9ae728a54bf6f0b06d","tid":2024543,"uid":235316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"r